## üìû Getting Help

**Documentation unclear?**
- Post in [GitHub Discussions](https://github.com/Toy-Department/CCM-Digitizing-Arm/discussions)
- Label as "documentation" + "question"

**Found an error?**
- File issue on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/Toy-Department/CCM-Digitizing-Arm/issues)
- Label as "documentation" + "bug"

**Want to improve docs?**
- Fork repository
- Edit markdown files
- Submit pull request
- See [README.md - Contributing](README.md#contributing)

